# How to restore VM for ColossusCloud


In order to do restoration for ColossusCloud, please follow the below steps:

- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Manage your Vms" 
- Click "Settings of the VM" you need
- Click "Actions" and click "Snapshot/Backups"
- Scroll down and you can see a list of all available snapshots for this VM.
- Then select the snapshot and click on the restore button to proceed with the restoration.
- 
- If you wish to restore a snapshot, be aware that this process will shut down your VM and will replace its disk with the snapshot.
